quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  39,11,"Boola mbu: “Esie ndalomesibwa okhulaama Nyasaye nemutswenulila Idini."
  39,12,"Ne ndalomesibwa mbu embe weyimbeli mubasalamu.”"
  39,13,"Boola mbu: “Esie eritsaanga eshinyasio shia inyanga ikhongo nekhaya okhuloonda ka Nyasaye wanje Omulesi.”"
  39,14,"Boola mbu: “Ni Nyasaye butswa niwenaamanga nemutswenushila mu dini yanje."
  39,15,"Kho laame shia mwenya owulali Ye tawe.” Boola mbu: “Toto abatiba ni balia beetibia abeene nende abandu babu inyanga yeyindukho. Koo, manye mbu okho nikho okhutiba khwa habulafu.”"
  39,16,"Baliba nende emibunjikho chiomulilo hekulu nende hasi wabu. Endio nilwa Nyasaye arisinjia Abasumba bebe. Enywe abasumba banje khaarie."
  39,17,"Ne balia basita ehale nende bioosi ebilali Nyasaye; khobalabilama tawe, mana nibakalukha khu Nyasaye, bali nende eshikhoyero, kho boolera abasumba banje akeshikhoyero."
  39,18,"Balia bawulilanga amakhuwa mana baloonda lilai muno liako. Abo nibo ba Nyasaye yalunjisia. Ne abo nibo bamachesi."
  39,19,"Ne koo, ulia wamala okhukhoyeshela okhunyoola likhuwa lieshinyasio (shia Nyasaye), mana ewe oli nobunyali bwokhuhabina uli mumulilo?"
  39,20,"Halali balia baria Nyasaye wabu Omulesi balinyoola tsigorofa ebikoro biombakhwa hekulu webindi, emialo chiburanga hasi watsio. Ino niindache ya Nyasaye, ne Nyasaye shakalukhasinjia indache yiye tawe."
  39,21,"Koo, shololangakhwo mbu Nyasaye yeshia amaatsi okhurula mwikulu, mana nakabusia mutsifututu mwiloba, mana nakamesilia emimela chiaukhane obukondo, mana chiume chikalukhane chibe namabuyu, mana achikhole amasakaria. Toto mu ako shilimwo eshitsulisio khubandu bamachesi."